    "ron_burgundy_voice": "Well, this is quite the pickleball exhibition. A lot of hitting, a lot of waiting. It seems they're very good at keeping the ball in play, which is... a strategy. And then, a ball goes into the net. Fascinating. Truly, a spectacle for the ages.",
